        principle: "Lab glassware aam taur par **Borosilicate glass (jaise Pyrex ya Borosil)** ka bana hota hai. Iska chayan isliye kiya jaata hai kyunki ismein **low coefficient of thermal expansion** hota hai. Iska matlab hai ki jab ise tezi se garam ya thanda kiya jaata hai, toh yeh aam kaanch ki tarah failta ya sikudta nahi hai, jisse yeh **thermal shock-resistant** banta hai aur achanak taapman badlav se tootta (crack) nahi hai. Iske alawa, yeh **chemical-resistant** bhi hota hai, yaani yeh adhikansh acids, alkalis, aur solvents ke saath react nahi karta, jisse sample ki shuddhta bani rehti hai. Glassware ko 'Class A' ya 'Class B' mein classify kiya jaata hai jo unki volumetric accuracy (sateekta) ko darshata hai.",
