        principle: "Adhikansh tezi se kaam karne wale milk analyzers <strong>ultrasonic technology</strong> (dhwani tarangon) ke siddhant par kaam karte hain. Upkaran doodh ke sample se ek **high-frequency ultrasonic signal (dhwani tarang)** guzarta hai. Doodh ke alag-alag components (jaise fat globules, dissolved proteins, lactose) is ultrasonic signal ki **gati (velocity)**, **shakti (amplitude)**, aur anya **acoustic properties** ko alag-alag tarike se prabhavit karte hain. Iske alawa, upkaran doodh ke **temperature** aur **conductivity** ko bhi maapta hai. Ek **internal microprocessor** in sabhi maape gaye parameters (signal changes, temperature, etc.) ko ek complex algorithm aur pre-calibrated data ke saath analyze karta hai. Is analysis ke aadhar par, yeh doodh ke composition (Fat%, SNF%, etc.) ka sateek anuman (estimation) lagata hai aur use digital screen par display karta hai.",
