        principle: "Yeh <strong>thermo-gravimetric</strong> siddhant par kaam karta hai (yaani, garmi se vajan mein kami). Yeh upkaran do cheezon ko jodta hai: ek **sateek analytical balance (tolne ki machine)** aur ek **shaktishali heating unit (aam taur par Halogen lamp ya Infrared heater)**.\n1.  User sample (jaise 2-3 gram milk powder) ko ek aluminum pan par failakar balance par rakhta hai aur 'Start' dabata hai. Machine sample ka shuruaati vajan (initial weight) record karti hai.\n2.  Halogen lamp turant chalu ho jaata hai aur sample ko tezi se garam karke usse paani ko **evaporate (bhaap bana kar uda)** deta hai.\n3.  Is dauran, balance lagatar sample ke vajan ko monitor karta hai. Jaise-jaise paani udta hai, vajan kam hota jaata hai.\n4.  Jab machine detect karti hai ki vajan sthir ho gaya hai (yaani, aur paani nahi ud raha hai), toh woh heating band kar deti hai. \n5.  Upkaran shuruaati vajan aur antim vajan ke antar se **vajan mein hui kami (jo nami thi)** ko calculate karke, moisture content ko seedhe percentage (%) mein display kar deta hai.",
